  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effects of nutritional therapy in elderly
      malnourished patients. The hypothesises are that nutritional supplementation and dietary
      advice alone or in combination affects mortality, quality of life and health-care consumption
      after six month of treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
